559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/ea4ab/me.jpg 700w,\n/static/ebfeb559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/3055e/me.jpg 1050w,\n/static/ebfeb559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/e901d/me.jpg 1079w","srcWebp":"/static/ebfeb559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/89afa/me.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/ebfeb559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/9fca7/me.webp 175w,\n/static/ebfeb559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/37a4e/me.webp 350w,\n/static/ebfeb559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/89afa/me.webp 700w,\n/static/ebfeb559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/78e7a/me.webp 1050w,\n/static/ebfeb559a8a4e95db0eba33bef75d3fd/b3e5f/me.webp 1079w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"skills":["JavaScript","Python3","React","Redux","express","Flask","PostgreSQL","Node","HTML/CSS","Git","AWS","Docker"]},"html":"<p>Oh my, where to begin...\nI've made quite the career-switch, coming from the entertainment industry, being signed with <a href=\"https://www.nextmanagement.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Next Models, Worldwide</a> where I worked for many popular brands and global media companies.</p>\n<p>Pioneering through the early stages of Social Media, I've amounted to over 500,000 followers spread-out amongst Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, YouTube, Snapchat, etc.</p>\n<p>I'm currently unemployed, in search of my first Junior Developer role.</p>\n<p>Here is a list of the technologies that I'm familiar with!</p>"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Freelance Content Writer","company":"Pepper","range":"July 2021 - Present","url":"https://www.peppercontent.io"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Creating Tech Content as a freelancer for the content giant <a href=\"https://www.peppercontent.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Pepper Content</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Submitted tech blogs on various popular topics for American Technology Consulting in 2500 words with a rating of 4.5/5.0.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Submitted a White Paper for Nous Infosystems in 1500 words with a rating of 5.0/5.0.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>View all my submitted articles and blogs <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1e8rnyb-r07s6Ss8QInvjiLU4rhJAYTCZ?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Software Developer","company":"Amdocs","range":"July 2020 - Present","url":"https://www.amdocs.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Responsible for code development, UAT support, automation of Bell Canada NM1-RTB customisation project as part of Digital Delivery scrum team. (Oct 2021 - present)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Part of Walk-the-Tech Go team of 10 developers building a microservice in Go language. Tech stack includes Couchbase, Go echo framework, REST APIs implementation, JMeter and Postman for testing purposes.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Selected as one of the 15 Amdocs India Innovation Agents with the least industry experience in years.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Responsible for code development as a developer of Amdocs Technology BSS-B2B Billing &#x26; RTB scrum team. (Nov 2020 - Oct 2021)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Certified in Agile, <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/133QWdIhw9KI0YMKs1SPI_6VQ1ENtMiCe/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">DevOps</a>, and MS360 architecture.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Technical Writer","company":"iSmile Tech","range":"July 2020 - August 2020","url":"https://www.ismiletechnologies.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Drafted all the website content and promotional templates on HubSpot for the startup.</li>\n<li>Reviewed the tech blogs and helped the Sales &#x26; Marketing Team.</li>\n<li>View <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1xc4SHoXSFWmLQfwBeYq7WwB5EjXsqMV9/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CERTIFICATE</a> and <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FVNB7SLHLwWB_QOSZFxIiSdy8O6Xbj2w/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">PERFORMANCE REVIEW REPORT</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Systems Intern","company":"CCL","range":"May - June 2019","url":"http://www.centralcoalfields.in/ind/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Project on developing a fully working dynamic eCommerce website using PHP and MySQL.</li>\n<li>Prepared a complete report about the specifications and working of the software.</li>\n<li>View <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Cn6gxJ1UYpcdz97FivBBp-SsXiVbgg5-/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">PROJECT REPORT</a> and <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1R1in-IgfDj9qx9btWEeA_9Ob3db-54_c/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CERTIFICATE</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Research Intern","company":"XLRI","range":"May - June 2018","url":"https://www.xlri.ac.in/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Meta analysis and a literature review on the topics 'Knowledge Hiding', 'Ethical Leadership', 'Ethical Culture', 'Ethical Climate' and 'Unethical Behaviour'.</li>\n<li>Maintained the data in MS Excel and represented the trend via R programming.</li>\n<li>Work done under Prof. Jatinder Kr. Jha of HR department of XLRI.</li>\n<li>View <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RlOPvA1EmE24aQMWeSiXbB3N36CUizXA/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CERTIFICATE</a></li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Critter","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='212'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20212'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M0%20106v106h22c21%200%2021%200%2025-2%206-4%207-6%201-3h-3c1-3%200-2-3%200-2%202-4%203-4%201%200-1%203-4%208-6%206-3%205-4-2-2l-5%202c0-1%206-5%208-5l3-1c1-1-1-1-6-1-7%201-7%201-4-1l4-3%206-1%206-2c1-1%201-1-1-1-4%202-15%202-15%201l5-1c5%200%208-1%208-2H38c-1-1%200-1%204-1l7-1c1-2%201-2-3-3-7-1-7-2%200-2l8-1-3-1-3-1c-1-1%200-1%203-1%2